https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hkhoi/bachelor_thesis/feature/blob_label/etc/screenshot01.png
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CvspEdX9Vr0

How To Build
-------------

	cd bachelor_thesis
	make
	make link

Executable binary is located in bin/, object files are located in obj/

Modules
-----------------
	main:		Entry point for the core application.
	cvutil:		OpenCV library wrapper.
	debug:		Plays the role like Android Log.d().
	vibe:		Foreground segmenter.
	blob:		Model for binary blobs.
	const:		Contains constants for the project.
	contour:	Contains Contour's definition.
	extractor:	Extract Blobs of Interest.
	tracker:	Keeps track of binary blobs.
	stat:		Retrieves data from expired blobs for learning purposes.

General Architecture
--------------------
		------------------
		| Frame Sequence |
		------------------
			|
			v
		-----------------
		| Current Frame |
		-----------------
			|
			|
			v
		***************
		* ViBE Module *
		***************
			|
			|
			v
		---------------------	
		|    Foreground     |
		---------------------
			|
			v
		********************
		* Extractor Module *<------------
		********************		|
			|			|
			|			|
			v			|
		-----------------------	   ------------
		| Blobs of Interest   |	   | Learning |
		-----------------------	   ------------
			|			|
			|			|
			v			|
		******************        ***************
		* Tracker Module *------->* Stat Module *
		******************        ***************
			|
			|
			|
			v
		******************
		* Counter Module *
		******************


